%pyspark
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import numpy as np
import pandas as pd
from pyspark.ml.regression import LinearRegression
from pyspark.ml.feature import VectorAssembler
from pyspark.ml.feature import StandardScaler
from pyspark.ml import Pipeline
from pyspark.sql.functions import *

# 'date == "2017-04-13" or date == "2017-05-01" or date == "2017-05-02" or date == "2017-05-17" or date == "2017-05-22" or date == "2017-05-25" or date == "2017-06-02" or date == "2017-06-05" or date == "2017-06-09" or date == "2017-06-14" or date == "2017-06-15" or date == "2017-06-20" or date == "2017-06-22" or date == "2017-09-01" or date == "2017-09-10" or date == "2017-09-12" or date == "2017-09-13" or date == "2017-09-14" or date == "2017-09-21" or date == "2017-09-28" or date == "2017-10-21" or date == "2017-10-30" or date == "2017-10-31" or date == "2017-11-11" or date == "2017-11-16" or date == "2017-12-13" or date == "2017-12-27" or date == "2018-01-06" or date == "2018-02-17" or date == "2018-02-25" or date == "2018-03-10" or date == "2018-03-31" or date == "2018-04-07" or date == "2018-04-09" or date == "2018-04-12" or date == "2018-04-13"'

%pyspark
df_nt = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///ds/nt_srs.parquet')
df_uv = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///ds/uv_srs.parquet')
df_wtob = spark.read.parquet('hdfs:///ds/wtob.parquet')
df_nt.cache()
df_uv.cache()
df_wtob.cache()

udf_dt2date = udf(lambda s: s.split(" ")[0])
udf_dt2time = udf(lambda s: s.split(" ")[1][:5])
udf_dt2month = udf(lambda s: int(s.split("-")[1]))

def dt2weather(datetime):
    month = int(datetime.split('-')[1])
    if 3 <= month <= 5:
        return 'spring'
    elif 6 <= month <= 8:
        return 'summer'
    elif 9 <= month <= 11:
        return 'fall'
    elif month == 12 or month <= 2:
        return 'winter'

udf_dt2weather = udf(dt2weather)

dt2weather('2017-12-13')

%pyspark

# You can specify multiple conditions in filter
# using OR (||) or AND (&&)

illum = df_nt.select('date', 'time', 'illum')\
             .filter('date == "2017-04-13" or date == "2017-05-01" or date == "2017-05-02" or date == "2017-05-17" or date == "2017-06-02" or date == "2017-06-05" or date == "2017-06-15" or date == "2017-09-13" or date == "2017-09-14" or date == "2017-09-21" or date == "2017-09-28" or date == "2017-10-21" or date == "2017-10-30" or date == "2017-10-31" or date == "2017-11-11" or date == "2017-11-16" or date == "2017-12-13" or date == "2017-12-27" or date == "2018-01-06" or date == "2018-02-17" or date == "2018-02-25" or date == "2018-03-10" or date == "2018-03-31" or date == "2018-04-07" or date == "2018-04-09" or date == "2018-04-12" or date == "2018-04-13"')

uvi = df_wtob.withColumn('date', udf_dt2date(df_wtob.datetime))\
             .withColumn('time', udf_dt2time(df_wtob.datetime))\
             .withColumn('weather', udf_dt2weather(df_wtob.datetime))\
             .withColumn('month', udf_dt2month(df_wtob.datetime))\
             .drop('datetime')\
             .select('date', 'month', 'time', 'weather', 'uvindex')\
             .filter('date == "2017-04-13" or date == "2017-05-01" or date == "2017-05-02" or date == "2017-05-17" or date == "2017-06-02" or date == "2017-06-05" or date == "2017-06-15" or date == "2017-09-13" or date == "2017-09-14" or date == "2017-09-21" or date == "2017-09-28" or date == "2017-10-21" or date == "2017-10-30" or date == "2017-10-31" or date == "2017-11-11" or date == "2017-11-16" or date == "2017-12-13" or date == "2017-12-27" or date == "2018-01-06" or date == "2018-02-17" or date == "2018-02-25" or date == "2018-03-10" or date == "2018-03-31" or date == "2018-04-07" or date == "2018-04-09" or date == "2018-04-12" or date == "2018-04-13"')

df_iluv = illum.join(uvi, ['date', 'time'])
df_iluv.createOrReplaceTempView('iluv')

illum.createOrReplaceTempView('illum')
uvi.createOrReplaceTempView('uvi')

order by date, time

%pyspark
from pyspark.ml.feature import VectorAssembler

assembler = VectorAssembler(inputCols=['illum'],
                            outputCol='features')

viluvb = assembler.transform(iluvb)

viluvb = viluvb.select('features', 'uvb')
viluvb.show()

train_test = viluvb.randomSplit([0.9, 0.1])
train = train_test[0]
test = train_test[1]

%pyspark
from pyspark.ml.regression import LinearRegression

lr = LinearRegression(featuresCol='features',
                      labelCol='uvb',
                      maxIter=10, regParam=0.3,
                      elasticNetParam=0.8)

lr_model = lr.fit(train)
summary = lr_model.summary

print('Coefficients: %.2f' % lr_model.coefficients[0])
print('Intercept: %.2f' % lr_model.intercept)
print('RMSE = %.2f' % summary.rootMeanSquaredError)
print('r2 = %.2f' % summary.r2)
